&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=46532&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=46532&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The problem appears to be that the messageExceptions array in the MailSendException class is not initialized unless the following constructor is used:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;public MailSendException(Map failedMessages) &lt;/p&gt;
{ ... }</comment>
